### 📊 Başarı Metrikleri (North Star + OKR)
```
🌟 North Star Metric
• "Tekrarlayan müşteri oranı" (30 günde 2+ satın alma)

📈 AARRR Metrikleri
• Acquisition: CAC < ₺150, organik trafik %40+
• Activation: İlk satın alma < 7 gün, onboarding completion > 60%
• Retention: 30-day retention > 35%, churn < 5%/ay
• Revenue: AOV > ₺450, LTV:CAC > 3:1
• Referral: K-faktörü > 0.5, NPS > 50

🎯 HEART Metrikleri (UX Kalitesi)
• Happiness: CSAT > 4.5/5, App Store rating > 4.7
• Engagement: Session duration > 4dk, pages/session > 5
• Adoption: Yeni özellik kullanım oranı > 30%
• Retention: 90-day active users growth > 15%/çeyrek
• Task Success: Checkout completion > 85%, hata oranı < 1%
```

