• Auth: JWT + refresh token rotation (HTTP-only cookie)
• Validation: Class-validator + DTO pattern
• Database: PostgreSQL 15 (Prisma ORM)
• Cache: Redis (session + ürün listesi cache)
• Search: Elasticsearch 8 (temel product indexing)
• Queue: BullMQ (e-posta gönderimi async)
• Storage: AWS S3 (görseller) + CloudFront CDN
```

### DevOps & Güvenlik
```
• Container: Docker + docker-compose (local/staging)
• CI/CD: GitHub Actions (test → build → deploy to staging)
• Monitoring: Sentry (error tracking) + Logtail (log aggregation)
• Security: Helmet.js, CORS policy, rate limiter (express-rate-limit)
• Backup: pg_dump daily cron + S3 versioning
• Environment: .env + dotenv-flow (dev/staging/prod ayrımı)
```

